2026-02-03T18:31:59.8988849Z 	
2026-02-03T18:31:59.8988977Z 	EOF
2026-02-03T18:31:59.8989101Z     fi
2026-02-03T18:31:59.8989235Z     esac
2026-02-03T18:31:59.8989360Z fi
2026-02-03T18:31:59.8989433Z 
2026-02-03T18:31:59.8989561Z # if the command-not-found package is installed, use it
